# OpenFork Desktop Quick Commands

Full documentation: `README.md`.

## Development

```powershell
cd ..\client
python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\python -m pip install -r requirements.txt

cd ..\desktop
npm install
npm run dev:all
```

Equivalent split terminals:

```powershell
npm run dev
npm run start
```

## Package

```powershell
npm run build
npm run pack
```

## Release

```powershell
npm run release
```
